ur email address.'</span><span style="color: #339933;">,</span></div></li><li style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align:top;"><div style="font: normal normal 1em/1.2em monospace; margin:0; padding:0; background:none; vertical-align:top;">            <span style="color: white;">'email.email'</span> <span style="color: #339933;">=&gt;</span> <span style="color: white;">'Please enter a valid email address.'</span><span style="color: #339933;">,</span></div></li><li style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align:top;"><div style="font: normal normal 1em/1.2em monospace; margin:0; padding:0; background:none; vertical-align:top;">            <span style="color: white;">'password.required'</span> <span style="color: #339933;">=&gt;</span> <span style="color: white;">'Please enter a password.'</span><span style="color: #339933;">,</span></div></li><li style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align:top;"><div style="font: normal normal 1em/1.2em monospace; margin:0; padding:0; background:none; vertical-align:top;">            <span style="color: white;">'password.min'</span> <span style="color: #339933;">=&gt;</span> <span style="color: white;">'The password must be at least 8 characters.'</span><span style="color: #339933;">,</span></div></li><li style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align:top;"><div style="font: normal normal 1em/1.2em monospace; margin:0; padding:0; background:none; vertical-align:top;">        <span style="color: #009900;">&#93;</span><span style="color: #339933;">;</span></div></li><li style="font-weight: bold; vertical-align:top;"><div style="font: normal normal 1em/1.2em monospace; margin:0; padding:0; background:none; vertical-align:top;">&nbsp;</div></li><li style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align:top;"><div style="font: normal normal 1em/1.2em monospace; margin:0; padding:0; background:none; vertical-align:top;">        <span style="color: red;">$request</span><span style="color: #339933;">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #004000;">validate</span><span s